---
// PaymentSection — Formas de pago aceptadas
---

<section id="pagos" class="payment-section section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-subtitle">💰 Formas de Pago</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Paga como prefieras</h2>
    <p class="payment-section__description">
      Aceptamos múltiples métodos de pago para tu comodidad. Todos tus datos están protegidos con encriptación SSL.
    </p>

    <div class="payment-section__grid">
      <div class="payment-card">
        <div class="payment-card__icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="1" y="4" width="22" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="1" y1="10" x2="23" y2="10"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="payment-card__title">Tarjetas de Crédito</h3>
        <p class="payment-card__text">Visa, Mastercard, American Express y más. Hasta 12 cuotas sin interés.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="payment-card">
        <div class="payment-card__icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="1" y="4" width="22" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="1" y1="10" x2="23" y2="10"/>
            <path d="M8 16h8"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="payment-card__title">Tarjetas de Débito</h3>
        <p class="payment-card__text">Débito automático desde tu cuenta bancaria. Rápido y seguro.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="payment-card">
        <div class="payment-card__icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 1a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 006 0V4a3 3 0 00-3-3z"/>
            <path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 01-14 0v-2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="23"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="23" x2="16" y2="23"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="payment-card__title">Transferencia Bancaria</h3>
        <p class="payment-card__text">Transferencia inmediata con descuento especial. CBU y alias disponibles.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="payment-card">
        <div class="payment-card__icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 015.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="payment-card__title">Criptomonedas</h3>
        <p class="payment-card__text">Bitcoin, Ethereum y USDT. Paga desde tu wallet de forma segura.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .payment-section {
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
  }

  .payment-section__description {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: -1.5rem auto var(--space-2xl);
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  .payment-section__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .payment-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .payment-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary-light);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .payment-card__icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);
  }

  .payment-card:hover .payment-card__icon {
    background: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .payment-card:hover .payment-card__icon svg {
    stroke: white !important;
  }

  .payment-card__title {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .payment-card__text {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
